  <brief_title>Treatment of High Blood Pressure Using Olmesartan With Hydrochlorothiazide Compared to an ACE Inhibitor With a Calcium Channel Blocker</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Study on the Efficacy and Safety of Olmesartan Medoxomil and Its Combination With Hydrochlorothiazide Compared With an ACE Inhibitor and Its Combination With a Calcium Channel Blocker in Patients With Stage 2 Hypertension</official_title>
  <sponsors>
